items.name: Energy From Within
explicitMods: 6% increased maximum Energy Shield
Increases and Reductions to Life in Radius are Transformed to apply to Energy Shield
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The Azmeri ascetics learnt the power
of going without the body's ordinary cravings.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: 5% increased maximum Energy Shield
5% increased maximum Life
5% increased maximum Mana
25% chance to Impale Enemies on Hit with Attacks while using Pride
Damage Penetrates 13% Lightning Resistance while affected by Wrath
Non-Channelling Skills have -10 to Total Mana Cost while affected by Clarity
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.

items.name: Forbidden Flesh
explicitMods: Allocates Deadly Infusion if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flame
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The bodies of those wholly subsumed by the Tangle
continue to merge and mutate and cry out for release...

items.name: Forbidden Flame
explicitMods: Allocates Deadly Infusion if you have the matching modifier on Forbidden Flesh
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The minds of those studied utterly by the Cleansing Fire
continue to think and dream and beg for silence...

items.name: Vivid Splinter
enchantMods: 2 Added Passive Skills are Jewel Sockets
Added Small Passive Skills grant: 10% increased Spell Damage
explicitMods: Added Small Passive Skills also grant: +3 to All Attributes
1 Added Passive Skill is Conjured Wall
1 Added Passive Skill is Essence Rush
1 Added Passive Skill is Practiced Caster
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Large Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Added passives do not interact with jewel radiuses. Right click to remove from the Socket.

items.name: Militant Faith
explicitMods:
Carved to glorify 3611 new faithful converted by High Templar Dominus
Passives in radius are Conquered by the Templars
+2% to all Elemental Resistances per 10 Devotion
1% reduced Mana Cost of Skills per 10 Devotion
Historic
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: They believed themselves the utmost faithful, but that conviction became oppression.

items.name: Stormshroud
explicitMods: +13% to Lightning Resistance
Modifiers to Chance to Avoid being Shocked apply to all Elemental Ailments
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: The true secret of the elements
is that all are one and the same.

reminderText: (Recently refers to the past 4 seconds)
